title: Bobby, Amy & Eddie Audition To Rap With Carrie Underwood + Lunchbox Breaks Up With His Post Office
itunes:title: Bobby, Amy & Eddie Audition To Rap With Carrie Underwood + Lunchbox Breaks Up With His Post Office
description:
Bobby, Amy and Eddie take turns rapping Ludacris’ verse in Carrie Underwood’s “The Champion.” Also, Lunchbox wears a hidden mic to break up with his post office after they up their prices.
